e offers her... One day, José spots Yaya, a street boy with the potential of a champion, and brings him to Belgium. Will Yaya be José's reward? Between the poor neighborhoods of Abidjan and Sporting Club of Charleroi, the cultural \"gap\" is brutal... and reserves surprises.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.1792,"vote_count":49,"poster_path":"/jAIT1neDejiOAb276mOWz2KwPp3.jpg","release_date":"2014-02-05","vote_average":4.7,"backdrop_path":"/hTp3I9vVm7zRmrHu2TmnqaA3H2S.jpg","original_title":"Les Rayures du Zèbre","original_language":"fr"},{"id":16774,"adult":false,"title":"Hellboy Animated: Sword of Storms","video":false,"overview":"A folklore professor becomes unwittingly possessed by the ancient Japanese demons of Thunder and Lightning. But when The Bureau of Paranormal Research & Defense dispatches a team of agents to investigate, a cursed samurai sword sends Hellboy to a supernatural dimension of ghosts, monsters, and feudal mayhem. Now while pyrokinetic Liz Sherman and fishboy Abe Sapien battle one very pissed-off dragon, a lost and cranky Hellboy must find his way home.","genre_ids":[878,16,14,28,27,12,53,10770],"popularity":1.465,"vote_count":148,"poster_path":"/vUCrcikFCDsvA6IiS59kdfQkseU.jpg","release_date":"2006-10-28","vote_average":6.236,"backdrop_path":"/d8VGgwr2WApwFewrL5yZQgo78E0.jpg","original_title":"Hellboy Animated: Sword of Storms","original_language":"en"},{"id":604563,"adult":false,"title":"OSS 117: From Africa with Love","video":false,"overview":"1981. Hubert Bonisseur de la Bath, aka OSS 117, is back. For this new mission – more delicate, more dangerous and more torrid than ever – he is forced to team up with a young new colleague, the promising OSS 1001.","genre_ids":[35,12,28],"popularity":1.1518,"vote_count":846,"poster_path":"/8KZun0DjBSVJtAEb7ytNKIKO0SL.jpg","release_date":"2021-08-04","vote_average":5.644,"backdrop_path":"/cZTVFoWr8teRlVLHSueMycnAJuQ.jpg","original_title":"OSS 117 : Alerte rouge en Afrique noire","original_language":"fr"},{"id":16249,"adult":false,"title":"Blackbeard's Ghost","video":false,"overview":"The eponymous wraith returns to Earth to aid his descendant, elderly Emily Stowecroft. The villains want to kick Emily and her friends out of their group home so that they can build a crooked casino. Good guy Steve Walker gets caught in the middle of the squabble after evoking Blackbeard's ghost.","genre_ids":[35,14,10751],"popularity":0.788,"vote_count":151,"poster_path":"/bEMEjagTsdkUi7Jzxe0lQsquD7J.jpg","release_date":"1968-02-08","vote_average":6.702,"backdrop_path":"/4bAsuQeYcLbUOzxXe407yEJQoF7.jpg","original_title":"Blackbeard's Ghost","original_language":"en"},{"id":17276,"adult":false,"title":"Carry On Up the Jungle","video":false,"overview":"The Carry On team send up the Tarzan tradition in great style. Lady Evelyn Bagley mounts an expedition to find her long-lost baby. Bill Boosey is the fearless hunter and guide. Prof. Tinkle is searching for the rare Oozalum bird. Everything is going swimmingly until a gorilla enters the camp, and then the party is captured by an all female tribe from Aphrodisia...","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.7297,"vote_count":61,"poster_path":"/r8zrAhPIwY6oh7IN4TZkNfFVPla.jpg","release_date":"1970-03-20","vote_average":5.82,"backdrop_path":"/z6dWuM72WkPsJVE475XhtYSE26q.jpg","original_title":"Carry On Up the Jungle","original_language":"en"},{"id":16441,"adult":false,"title":"The Beastmaster","video":false,"overview":"Dar, is the son of a king, who's hunted by a priest after his birth and grows up in another family. When he becomes a grown man, his new father is murdered by savages and he discovers that he's the ability to communicate with the animals, which leads him on his quest for revenge against his father's killers.","genre_ids":[14,12,28],"popularity":2.3965,"vote_count":443,"poster_path":"/ytaKNYpHdQnClTbWL2m19Xv6PXZ.jpg","release_date":"1982-08-16","vote_average":6.286,"backdrop_path":"/zHTnieWaWlObW2wLQO3ePkwHlom.jpg","original_title":"The Beastmaster","original_language":"en"},{"id":1489373,"adult":false,"title":"Lil' Bastard","video":true,"overview":"A half troll half barbarian is shrunk to the size of a rat and thrown into present day just to ruin everyone's life.","genre_ids":[27,35,14],"popularity":2.1062,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/fy5ob0M9KxLc7KwVADG4YWYnhn0.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-27","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Lil' Bastard","original_language":"en"},{"id":17762,"adult":false,"title":"Geisha Assassin","video":false,"overview":"One rainy night in the Edo period, Kotono (a geisha) confronts samurais who killed her father. The samurais attack her one after another, but she fights hard against samurais with her sword. Kotono tries to chase the samurais who scramble to escape. Yet now three ninjas stand up against her. Kotono drops her sword by their wave of assaults. Can she beat them?","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":0.4228,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/tMcoaWNR8nmNtGFS6vAhHYqAwmL.jpg","release_date":"2008-09-27","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/evrNkzM9jfeJeaecBOmLs60HQQo.jpg","original_title":"芸者ｖｓ忍者","original_language":"ja"},{"id":15587,"adult":false,"title":"Safari","video":false,"overview":"Richard Dacier owns a tour agency specialized on organizing safaris for European tourists eager to confront the African wild life. Actually, he took the job after his father and never went into the savanna by himself. As he owes big money to some mobster, he is compelled to convey a fake tourist, with a suspicious suitcase, toward Mozambic. To avoid suspicion from the authorities, he is supposed to tour a group of tourists as usual. The only problem - he is completely unexperienced as a guide!","genre_ids":[12,35],"popularity":0.5903,"vote_count":341,"poster_path":"/k3YyJ8SCHjYiVtL8dXn0sQzcEzU.jpg","release_date":"2009-04-01","vote_average":4.6,"backdrop_path":"/6HEwXKpci1B1cEPQdG3CBNAUNHt.jpg","original_title":"Safari","original_language":"fr"},{"id":266427,"adult":false,"title":"Vengeance","video":false,"overview":"John Meadham, in charge of a West African trading post, wires the home office in London that he is tired and worn out and that they need to send a replacement to take over. The company sends a stiff upper-lipper, Charles Summers, accompanied by his wife, Margaret. An antagonism develops between the two men from the moment Summers arrives.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,10749],"popularity":0.1657,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/jWK8Gin4LdbtXagJ5YckxHSoyyB.jpg","release_date":"1930-02-22","vote_average":3.3,"backdrop_path":"/yYhbLxCLxpfFR7xzCQV4At2D1tV.jpg","original_title":"Vengeance","original_language":"en"},{"id":16687,"adult":false,"title":"Wushu","video":false,"overview":"A group of Wushu students stumble into a child kidnapping ring run by an alumnus.","genre_ids":[18,28],"popularity":1.3835,"vote_count":21,"poster_path":"/xims8UJUe91CPnwobdNwpy1kIMK.jpg","release_date":"2008-10-23","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/g72VJgY8reM1zqAPBOsSJVd1f5l.jpg","original_title":"武术之少年行","original_language":"zh"},{"id":19386,"adult":false,"title":"He-Man and She-Ra: The Secret of the Sword","video":false,"overview":"After experiencing traumatic nightmares of a time now past, the Sorceress summons Prince Adam and Cringer to Castle Grayskull to give Adam a precious, jeweled sword and send the pair to the planet Etheria to investigate its secrets.","genre_ids":[16,28,12,10751,14],"popularity":1.2667,"vote_count":90,"poster_path":"/iPU6h1EVljeoqIL5fZx4kSsXwLx.jpg","release_date":"1985-03-22","vote_average":6.578,"backdrop_path":"/1jSJMUigYZXVmIBARQxwU8rzArr.jpg","original_title":"He-Man and She-Ra: The Secret of the Sword","original_language":"en"},{"id":3484,"adult":false,"title":"The Mask of Fu Manchu","video":false,"overview":"The villainous Dr. Fu Manchu races against a team of Englishmen to find the tomb of Ghengis Khan, because he wants to use the relics to cause an uprising in the East to wipe out the white race.","genre_ids":[